description:
&lt;p&gt;AGH Solutions Limited is a subsidiary of Airedale NHS Foundation Trust and provides a range of services to the Trust. We have opportunities for reliable, enthusiastic, people centred and caring individuals to join our Switchboard team to provide a high quality standard of service to ensure a positive patient experience.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The successful candidates will work on the Telephonist Bank to communicate effectively with patients, work colleagues and visitors throughout the process of delivery of the service&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is a casual zero hours contact that could include evenings and weekend working. Applicants must have experience of working with a diverse cross section of the community and the public in general. Previous experience is not essential but you must be able to align to the following values:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Compassion&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Commitment to quality of service&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Respect and Dignity&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Kath Aspinall, Head of Procurement &amp; Supplies on 01535 294896.&lt;/p&gt;
